   ``Eyewitness to War,'' prints and daguerreotypes of the Mexican
War, 1846-1848. Through Jan. 14.
   ``American Prints: Recent Acquisitions.'' Through Feb. 18.
   
   Kimbell Art Museum:
   ``The Consul Smith Collection: Rafael to Canaletto Masterpieces
From the Royal Library, Windsor Castle.'' Through Jan. 21.
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>MESA, Ariz</BYLINE>
